quote.summary: Landsea Green Life Service Co Ltd is an investment holding company primarily engaged in the provision of property management services. The Company mainly operates four businesses. The property management services business is engaged in providing property management services, including security, cleaning, gardening and landscaping, car parking management, and daily repair and maintenance services. The value-added services to non-property owners business is engaged in providing sales assistance services, property consultancy services and other pre-delivery services, and property agency services. The community value-added services business is engaged in providing home-living services, public resource management services and asset management services for properties. The apartment operation and management services business is engaged in providing apartment operation and management services. The Company mainly conducts its business in the domestic market.
